====Adjective====
{{nl-adj|heler}}

# [[complete]], [[full]], [[whole]]

=====Inflection=====
{{nl-decl-adj|hele}}

=====Synonyms=====
* {{l|nl|gans}}
* {{l|nl|volledig}}

=====Derived terms=====
* {{l|nl|geheel}}
* {{l|nl|helen}}

=====Related terms=====
* {{l|nl|heil}}

====Adverb====
{{nl-adv}}

# [[very]]

=====Usage notes=====
Although an adverb, {{m|nl||heel}} may be inflected as well ({{m|nl|hele}}) to match the following adjective. For example, both of these sentences are correct:
* {{ux|nl|Dat is een '''heel''' grote boom.|That is a '''very''' large tree.}}
* {{ux|nl|Dat is een '''hele''' grote boom.|That is a '''very''' large tree.}}
The latter form may be regarded as informal and less appropriate for formal writing.

